## Development

```bash
uv sync
uv run pre-commit install   # optional: run the lint stack on every commit
uv run pytest
uv run mypy src
```

Linting (ruff, [zizmor](https://docs.zizmor.sh/), mdformat) runs via [pre-commit](https://pre-commit.com); CI runs the same stack plus mypy and pytest via the shared [`python-ci`](https://github.com/{{ github_owner }}/python-project-template) reusable workflow.
